<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>404 - Page Not Found</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f6f9fc, #e4ecf7);
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      height: 100vh;
      overflow: hidden;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }

    .container {
      text-align: center;
      animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes float {
      0%, 100% {
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
      50% {
        transform: translateY(-10px);
      }
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 120px;
      margin: 0;
      color: #e74c3c;
      letter-spacing: 5px;
    }

    h2 {
      margin: 10px 0;
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #555;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    a {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #2980b9;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 25px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    a:hover {
      background-color: #1f6391;
    }

    .ghost {
      font-size: 80px;
      animation: blink 2s infinite;
    }

    @keyframes blink {
      0%, 100% {
        opacity: 1;
      }
      50% {
        opacity: 0.3;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="ghost">üëª</div>
    <h1>404</h1>
    <h2>Oops! Page Not Found</h2>
    <p>The page you‚Äôre looking for doesn‚Äôt exist or has been moved.</p>
    <a href="/">‚Üê Back to Home</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
